attr.title: Void Call
attr.desc: They said, "This is your last chance." I didn't care. The prototype R0-Z -- the first working time machine -- fell to MAGNUM CA, a space paramilitary at odds with my employer. My job is to steal it; my mission is my own. I'm done being their pawn. I won't let them keep it, and I won't use it. I'll let the void take it.
attr.inst: Download VoidCall_Update.zip from itch.io (https://louiechapm.itch.io/void-call). Copy VoidCall_exe.zip to voidcall port folder
attr.inst_md: Download **VoidCall_Update.zip** from [itch.io](https://louiechapm.itch.io/void-call). Copy `VoidCall_exe.zip` to `voidcall` port folder
